All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Admin
The Admin class represents an administrator in the system, inheriting from the Staff class.
AdminController
AdminController is a controller class that acts as a "middleman" between the view classes - AdminView, DisplayStaffView and ManageStaffAccountView and the model class - Admin and Staff.
AdminView
The AdminView class represents the main interface for administrators in the hospital management system.
Appointment
The Appointment class represents a scheduled meeting between a Patient and a Doctor.
AppointmentController
The AppointmentController class is a controller class that acts as a "middleman" between the view classes - AdminView and DisplayAppointmentDetailView, and the model classes - Admin and Appointment.
AppointmentList
The AppointmentList class is a singleton that manages the list of appointments in the application.
AppointmentOutcome
The AppointmentOutcome class represents the outcome of a medical appointment, including prescribed medicines, diagnoses, services provided, and payment status.
AppointmentOutcomeController
The AppointmentOutcomeController class manages operations related to appointment outcomes, specifically handling pending medicine prescriptions, approval, and inventory updates.
AppointmentOutcomeView
The AppointmentOutcomeView class handles the user interface for managing appointment outcomes.
AppointmentStatus
The AppointmentStatus enum represents the various states an appointment can be in within the hospital management system.
Diagnosis
The Diagnosis class represents a medical diagnosis for a patient.
DisplayAppointmentDetailView
The DisplayAppointmentDetailView class provides an interface for administrators to view details of specific appointments in the hospital management system.
DisplayDoctorAppointment
The DisplayDoctorAppointment class manages the doctor's interface for handling appointments.
DisplayMedicationInventory
The DisplayMedicationInventory class provides an interface for administrators to view the medical inventory in the hospital management system.
DisplayPatientAppointment
The DisplayPatientAppointment class manages the patient's interface for handling appointments.
DisplayStaffView
The DisplayStaffView class provides an interface for administrators to view hospital staff based on specific filters in the hospital management system.
Doctor
Represents a doctor in the hospital management system.
DoctorController
The DoctorController class provides methods for managing doctor-related operations, such as retrieving schedules, handling availability, managing specializations, and retrieving associated patients and appointments.
DoctorView
The DoctorView class provides the interface for doctors to manage their responsibilities.
FileType
The FileType enum represents different types of files used in the system.
Gender
An enumerator that corresponds to the different gender of the staff
Helper
A utility class that provides helper methods and utilities for common operations such as input validation, date-time processing, and user interaction.
Helper.TimeValidationRule
Enumeration for different time validation rules that can be combined
HMSApp
The starting point of the application.
HospitalManagementAppView
The HospitalManagementAppView class represents the main interface of the hospital management system.
InventoryController
InventoryController is a controller class that acts as a "middleman" between the view classes - AdminView, InventoryView, DisplayMedicalInventoryView ManageMedicalInventoryView and ManagReplenishmentRequestView and the model class - Admin, InventoryList and Medicine.
InventoryList
The InventoryList class represents an inventory item in the medical inventory system.
InventoryRequestStatus
An enumerator that corresponds to the different inventory request status
InventoryView
The InventoryView class provides an interface for pharmacists to view and manage the medication inventory in the hospital management system.
LoginView
The LoginView class provides an interface for handling user authentication for the hospital management system.
MainView
The MainView class is an abstract base class for all views in the hospital management system.
ManageMedicalInventory
The ManageMedicalInventory class provides an interface for administrators to manage the medical inventory in the hospital management system.
ManageReplenishmentRequestView
The ManageReplenishmentRequestView class provides an interface for administrators to manage replenishment requests in the hospital management system.
ManageStaffAccountView
The ManageStaffAccountView class provides an interface for administrators to manage hospital staff accounts in the hospital management system.
MedicalRecord
Represents the medical record of a patient in the hospital management system.
Medicine
 
MedicineStatus
The MedicineStatus enum represents the status of a medicine in the hospital management system.
OutOfRange
The OutOfRange exception is thrown to indicate that a token retrieved by a Scanner is not within the specified range.
Patient
Represents a patient in the hospital management system.
PatientController
The PatientController class provides functionality for managing patient-related operations, such as authentication, updating contact information, displaying personal information, viewing medical records, and retrieving appointment outcomes.
PatientView
The PatientView class provides an interface for patients to interact with the hospital management system.
PaymentController
The PaymentController class handles the logic for generating payment receipts, processing payments, and updating payment statuses for medical appointments.
PaymentStatus
The PaymentStatus enum represents the status of a payment in the hospital management system.
PaymentView
The PaymentView class handles the user interface for managing patient payments.
Pharmacist
The Pharmacist class represents a specific type of Staff member in the hospital management system.
PharmacistController
The PharmacistController class handles operations related to pharmacist authentication, password management, and submission of replenishment requests for inventory items.
PharmacistView
The PharmacistView class represents the user interface for pharmacists in the hospital management system.
ReplenishmentRequest
The ReplenishmentRequest class represents a request to replenish stock levels for a specific medicine.
Repository
The Repository class provides a centralized storage and management mechanism for all data in the hospital management system.
Schedule
Represents a schedule with a specific start time and end time.
ServiceType
The ServiceType enum represents different types of medical services offered in the hospital management system.
Specialization
Represents a specialization in a particular medical field or expertise.
Staff
The Staff class represents an employee in a hospital management system.
StaffController
StaffController is a controller class that acts as a "middleman" between the view classes - AdminView, PatientView, PharmacistView and View and the model class - Admin, Doctor, Patient, Pharmacist and Staff.
StaffType
An enumerator that corresponds to the different type of staff
Treatment
Represents a medical treatment associated with a diagnosis.
